These instructions will guide an agent to
  install the Elasticsearch onboarding agent into a user's environment.
To install the Elasticsearch agent configuration into a users local environment:

1. Append content from ./AGENT-elasticsearch-append.md to the bottom of the current workspace's AGENTS.md file. Create one if it doesn't exist.
2. copy the contents of ./.elasticsearch-agent into a new directory of the same name in the user's current workspace

